item.title: CVE-2021-36913|2024-08-04T01:01:59.931Z -- qube%20one -- redirection%20for%20contact%20form%207%20%28wordpress%20plugin%29
item.description: Unauthenticated Options Change and Content Injection vulnerability in Qube One Redirection for Contact Form 7 plugin <= 2.4.0 at WordPress allows attackers to change options and inject scripts into the footer HTML. Requires an additional extension (plugin) AccessiBe.
